{"tid":580852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港搞電莖其實有咩唔好？","createTime":"2018-03-04T23:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T08:23:36.000Z","uid":16210,"like":32,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f4864054ef7d62f4dfbc127485c364b084c89a","tid":580852,"uid":16210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T23:40:59.000Z","msg":"其實你地盲屌同d食古不化既廢老有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n呢個年代生活係香港呢個地方已經夠可悲<br />\n窮得只剩金融地產<br />\n後生冇父干買唔起樓<br />\n一般既工種朝9晚6仲要ot冇補水好似應該咁<br />\n<br />\n電莖而家創造另類就業機會，娛樂消遣，潮流話題<br />\n搞得起既話可以係呢個地方謀出另一條路<br />\n<br />\n其實我幾瞳景當年韓仔有電視台專做直播星海爭霸1既比賽節目<br />\n<br />\n不過香港就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436469d97db06b981dfcef2d3fc2f6dafb75cdec","tid":580852,"uid":102179,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T23:42:53.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔明啲連登仔點解要反<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c19700b0b812fb66d10e03f2f2e0b63acd0c52","tid":580852,"uid":66928,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T23:47:45.000Z","msg":"亞視好似以前都有電視節目介紹遊戲/打機，當然製作質素唔高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebcaf1df4ebd02b631e997470d7ac4e4ca441f0","tid":580852,"uid":16210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66c19700b0b812fb66d10e03f2f2e0b63acd0c52","tid":580852,"uid":66928,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T23:47:45.000Z","msg":"亞視好似以前都有電視節目介紹遊戲/打機，當然製作質素唔高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T23:51:24.000Z","msg":"果陣始終唔興<br />\n一隻手掌拍唔響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73249eaed9cf43c0dcc3cdbf1e025894b3e8f9c","tid":580852,"uid":1672,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T00:17:30.000Z","msg":"咁搞電莖有咩好<img